Magic =
Magic is one of the quickest ways to kill metal dragons cheaply, and can be done without taking damage.  All the caster has to do is make sure their [[antifire]] is active, [[anti-dragon shield]] is equipped and attack them at a distance.
Although players can opt for better setups if [[maging]], [[Void mage helm|Void mage]] can be used as well for accounts below 70 [[Defence]]. However, [[Ahrim's]] will prove to be better when players have level 70 [[Defence]] or higher.

